  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Residence Alpen Lodge provides self catered apartments. The apartments have well equipped kitchens including an induction hob, combi oven- microwave, toaster and kettle. There is a well stocked supermarket less than 100 metres from the residence. </p>
<p>Alternatively, we've partnered up with Huski who provide premium oven ready meals across the French Alps. Huski will deliver your meals directly to your accommodation in time for your arrival, all you'll have to do is cook. If you'd like to know more, please click <a data-udi="umb://document/341dc2e969e244a9a524ec35d94ae575" href="/{localLink:umb://document/341dc2e969e244a9a524ec35d94ae575}" title="Huski - food &amp; drink delivery service">here</a> for further details.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Residence Alpen Lodge has an ideal location in the Eucherts area of <a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" title="La Rosière">La Rosiere,</a> just by the Eucherts Express chairlift. The modern south-facing residence has top of the range facilities to make you stay easy and enjoyable. There are 33 stylish and spacious apartments, all with a equipped kitchen and large balcony.  After a day on the slopes,  you have use of the extensive wellness area - it is the perfect spot to relax.</p>
<h2>Fantastic location</h2>
<p>Being just 450 metres from the Eucherts Express chairlift, the ideal location allows you direct access to the fabulous <span>San Bernardo ski area - linking <a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" title="La Rosière">La Rosière</a> with </span>La Thuile, <span>it’s the only Franco-Italian ski area in the Northern Alps. </span></p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>The Alpen Lodge has a wonderful wellness area so you can pamper yourself with the steam room, sauna, whirlpools, Himalayan salt wall and sensory showers. There is also a panoramic pool with views of the valley. If you want to stay active, make the most of the cardio and fitness room. For the ultimate treat, massage and beauty treatments are also available to book locally. </p>
<h2>Food and drink</h2>
<p>These self catering apartments have everything you need for a winter getaway in <span><a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" title="La Rosière">La Rosière</a>, each apartment has a well equipped kitchen so you can whip up tasty meals from the comfort of your apartment. </span>This gives you a chance to sample some of the local cuisine each evening, there is a wide choice of Savoyard restaurants serving traditional fondue, raclette or t<span>artiflette </span><span>- being so close to the Italian border there is also plenty of restaurants serving Italian favourites including pizza and pasta.</span> For a bit of evening entertainment the M'Bar at the <a data-udi="umb://document/16eb7609caa2475eada3579b12130b79" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16eb7609caa2475eada3579b12130b79}" title="Alpen Lodge Hotel &amp; Spa">Alpen Lodge</a> hosts weekly music nights, whether it be jazz, blues or pop rock. </p>]]></description>
