  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p>Free use of the spa leisure facilities open all day from 10am to 8pm. There's a magnificent pool with separate children's pool, sauna, steam room, whirl pools, Himalayan salt wall and sensory showers.</p>
<p>Beauty treatments and massages are available, book and pay locally for these.</p>
<p>Additional facilities at the hotel include</p>
<ul>
<li>Bar &amp; lounge with log fire </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi throughout the residence</li>
<li>Children's play area (not supervised)</li>
<li>Luggage storage for early arrivals and late departures and assistance with luggage</li>
<li>On site restaurant</li>
<li>Indoor covered car parking space (one included per apartment)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
