  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two Bedroom Prestige Apartments</strong>  are around 65m² sleeping two to six people and have a double bedroom, twin bedroom, and living area with double sofa bed.</p>
<p>One linen set with towels is provided per person, per week. Beds are made up on arrival, apart from the sofa beds and end of stay cleaning is included except the kitchen.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Fully equipped kitchen with dishwasher, filter coffee-maker and Nespresso machine, induction hob, oven in integral microwave, toaster and kettle</li>
<li>Loan of Raclette, Fondue, Crêpe and Stone-Grill devices (subject to availability)</li>
<li>Spacious living area</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Bath or shower room</li>
<li>Two WCs</li>
<li>Bathrobes and slippers for adults</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
